    Local SEO, Google Ads, Websites und KI – die Hebel für mehr Anfragen aus Ihrer Region.
  </p>
  <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm">
    <li><a href="/local-seo/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Local SEO</a></li>
    <li><a href="/seo/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">SEO</a></li>
    <li><a href="/geo-aeo/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">GEO &amp; AEO</a></li>
    <li><a href="/google-ads/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Google Ads</a></li>
    <li><a href="/ads/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Online Marketing / Ads</a></li>
    <li><a href="/website-erstellung/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Website Erstellung</a></li>
    <li><a href="/google-business-profile/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Google Business Profile</a></li>
    <li><a href="/google-maps-optimierung/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Google Maps Optimierung</a></li>
    <li><a href="/ai/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">KI Lösungen</a></li>
    <li><a href="/lead-generierung/" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors">Lead Generierung</a></li>
